imdb.title: Ore ga ojô-sama gakkô ni 'shomin sample' toshite gettsu sareta ken
imdb.plot: A private all-girls school forcibly recruits an ordinary male student to help its female graduates adjust to the outside world.

episodes.title: Welcome, Commoner
episodes.plot: Kimito is carried away by some musclemen.

episodes.title: Reiko Is Who We Wish to Be Like
episodes.plot: What is everyday routine for Kimito is exotic to the girls.

episodes.title: It Was Like the Garden of Eden
The Tea Party Incident
episodes.plot: Some of the girls turn into drama queens.

episodes.title: Just Friends
episodes.plot: While having their fortunes told by Kimito's phone, the girls discover that it can also predict their compatibility with members of the opposite sex. After Kimito asks Kujo to stop waking him in her usual manner, she is reluctant.

episodes.title: Step Outside
episodes.plot: The class takes a field trip to the newly-completed theme park "Shominland," where the students get to experience the commoner lifestyle. Kimito coaches the others through almost, but not-quite-authentic commoner activities.

episodes.title: The Tsun-Pure in Her Element
episodes.plot: Whilst still on the school trip Aika has become extremely popular due to her knowledge of commoner culture.

episodes.title: Aika-sama Has a Lot of Friends
episodes.plot: Kimito introduces Aika to a fortune telling game on his cell phone.

episodes.title: Kagurazaka-sama Is Here
episodes.plot: Kimito introduces the girls to the concept of a Maid café which confuses the girls who are used to being surrounded by maids ever day.

episodes.title: I've Been Curious About This for a While, But What Is Gets?
episodes.plot: Kimito's attempt to pull a prank on the naïve Aika results in a new fad spreading throughout the entire school which, due to the students being cut off from popular culture, could last for up to ten years.

episodes.title: Is This Not the Sky That Kimito-sama Was Looking at?
episodes.plot: Reiko and Kimito share a pleasant moment together in the classroom.

episodes.title: Inexperienced Though I Am, Please Accept Me Forever
episodes.plot: Kimito, Karen, Aika, Hakua and Masaomi arrive at the meeting place which is heavily guarded.
